{"tid":2269331,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁家傑揭英國夏鼎基立法會特權法原意:  難怪外國話香港一國一制!","createTime":"2020-11-03T11:57:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T12:32:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e90e6b3c5c36a411998a0fc7995778d1f0f97d57","tid":2269331,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T11:57:38.000Z","msg":"#立法會 #特權法 #左右大局<br />\n<br />\n梁家傑揭英國夏鼎基立法會特權法原意: <br />\n難怪外國話香港一國一制! <br />\nD100 左右大局 <br />\n(主持: 梁家權、梁家傑)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JokMxCVbK5ESAVE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJokMxCVbK5ESAVE&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=7acbb1c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JokMxCVbK5ESAVE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nD100 Radio<br />\n511K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n梁家傑揭英國夏鼎基立法會特權法原意: 難怪外國話香港一國一制!  D100 左右大局 (主持: 梁家權、梁家傑)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特區警察周日 (1日) 起拘捕8名泛民主派人士，包括多名現任和前任立法會議員，指控他們今年5月擾亂立法會內務委員會一個特別會議，並揚言是據立法會權力及特權法下的罪名拘捕。屬泛民主派的前立法會議員梁家傑指出，特權法是香港主權移交前立法局在1985年通過，目的是防止行政機關干預立法會的運作，現在卻被當局用來檢控議員，形容做法「有政治目的」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nD100 香港: <a href=\"http://www.d100.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.d100.net&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=56317cf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.d100.net</a><br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/d100hk.m\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fd100hk.m&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=a63613c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/d100hk.m</a>"},{"pid":"44d5485e13a58a43869caed2f6e6341131fd4bff","tid":2269331,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T12:00:21.000Z","msg":"林鄭：行政機關冇乾乳<br />\n係執法機關乾乳<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb774fe6b2aefaa2bfeb1af1af3077c5b72db67","tid":2269331,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-1